  <data name="About_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>About this project</value></data>
  <data name="About_Intro" xml:space="preserve"><value>WorkPlan Studio is a small portfolio application for managing manufacturing routings (work plans): the sequence of operations needed to produce a part, the work centers they run on, and the resulting time and cost.</value></data>
  <data name="About_TechTitle" xml:space="preserve"><value>How it is built</value></data>
  <data name="About_Tech1" xml:space="preserve"><value>.NET 10 Blazor WebAssembly — ships as a static site, no backend required.</value></data>
  <data name="About_Tech2" xml:space="preserve"><value>EF Core with SQLite compiled to WebAssembly — a real relational database running in the browser.</value></data>
  <data name="About_Tech3" xml:space="preserve"><value>Your data is stored locally (localStorage) and never leaves your device.</value></data>
  <data name="About_Tech4" xml:space="preserve"><value>English / German interface via IStringLocalizer and .resx resources.</value></data>
